&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define project scope, requirements, and automation strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement automation solutions, including hardware and software design, programming, testing, and commissioning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform system integration and troubleshooting of PLCs, HMIs, and SCADA systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute commissioning activities, including job walks and onsite support in Southern California&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with regulatory and safety requirements throughout the project lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical guidance, troubleshooting support, and training to project teams and stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate and maintain project documentation including design specifications, test protocols, commissioning plans, and SOPs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
