&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Author and execute validation protocols for equipment and systems, including cleaning validation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Lead troubleshooting and data analysis for validation test results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Support tech transfers, equipment modifications, and requalification activities&lt;/li&gt;
