&lt;p&gt;Valspec—a global provider of system validation and lifecycle services—provides commissioning and qualification of computerized systems for clients in the Life Sciences industry. Established in 1999, Valspec&#39;s mission is to provide a wide spectrum of services that help its clients meet their capital project and lifecycle maintenance goals.&lt;/p&gt;
